02:45.260 --> 02:45.980
It really is.

02:45.980 --> 02:53.040
Now, if you are listening to that title and thinking, you know, wow, I need a degree in advanced mathematics just to get through the introduction, do not worry.

02:53.140 --> 02:55.080
That is exactly why we are here.

02:55.200 --> 02:55.300
Right.

02:55.400 --> 02:56.700
We're doing the heavy lifting for you.

