03:12.520 --> 03:13.520
It really is.

03:13.520 --> 03:16.260
We are exploring a radical proposition here.

03:16.900 --> 03:27.320
What if the way we've been writing, running, and understanding computer code since the dawn of the digital age is based on a fundamental illusion about how math actually works?

03:27.680 --> 03:29.740
It's a wildly compelling premise.

