I'm trying to picture this.

10:47.860 --> 10:52.080
If I have a sphere for five times four, all the multiplying happens in that bubble.

10:52.240 --> 10:57.280
The rest of the equation, the three times on the outside, has absolutely no idea what is going on inside the bubble.

10:57.400 --> 10:57.920
None at all.

10:57.980 --> 11:00.060
It just sees the opaque surface of the bubble.

11:00.260 --> 11:04.440
