if we want to see why this is different from traditional cod.

11:28.260 --> 11:29.120
So how is it different?

11:29.420 --> 11:33.100
Well, in traditional programming, evaluation is essentially a string rewrite rule.

11:33.220 --> 11:37.940
You find a string of text, like five times four, and you substitute it with a new string of text, 20.

