but the exact moment it pops, the finished protein is suddenly available for the next larger biological process to use.

12:23.320 --> 12:27.040
If we connect this to the bigger picture, this exact moment, the pop,

12:27.120 --> 12:31.800
is where the narrative of traditional computation and the sphere pop calculus diverge completely.

12:32.040 --> 12:32.420
How so?

