13:05.960 --> 13:14.220
Because SBC's absolute stubborn refusal to forget the past fundamentally changes the nature of what data even is.

13:14.340 --> 13:19.700
This brings us to what the monograph calls the missing object of traditional computer science.

13:19.800 --> 13:20.580
The missing object.

13:20.800 --> 13:21.020
Right.

13:21.520 --> 13:25.940
In historical systems, again, going back to Turing machines or the lambda calculus,

13:26.300 --> 13:29.020
the current state of the machine is the only thing that matters.

