14:05.820 --> 14:13.100
The fundamental primitive, the basic building block of all logic, is the irreversible history of how that state came to be.

14:13.320 --> 14:15.660
Think about the magnitude of that shift for a moment.

14:16.200 --> 14:21.140
The program is no longer a sequence of isolated, transient states replacing each other.

